Iran does not border any European countries

Iran is included in various reliable sources as being part of South Asia. Not only for statistical purposes as mentioned by the UNSD, but other sources as well. This UN source provided is from a different branch of the UN, not the UNSD. Read it carefully.  Even for statistical purposes, iran is still listed under South Asia. For statistical purposes, India is in South Asia. For statistical purposes, Pakistan is in South Asia. For statistical purposes, Afghanistan is in South Asia.
